These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, coffee, mirinda, lemonade, almond-milk
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, horse, goldfish, mouse, fish
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the owner of the horse is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
12. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | almond-milk | water    | soy-milk | coffee | lemonade |
| Pet        | rabbit      | fish  | goldfish | guinea-pig | mouse          | horse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, sprite, lemonade, soy-milk, water
There are 6 different nationalities: canadian, spanish, egyptian, brazilian, malaysian, french
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the canadian is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the malaysian is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is the egyptian##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking fanta##2
 8. the french is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the brazilian is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the malaysian is on the left or right of the spanish##3
12. the spanish is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
13. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
14. the egyptian is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | 7up  | lemonade     | fanta | sprite    | water       | soy-milk  |
| Nationality   | french | canadian | egyptian       | brazilian | spanish | malaysian |

