.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, coffee, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people have 6 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, hiking, photography, dancing, gardening
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person drinking milk##2
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | sprite     | milk | almond-milk        | iced-tea   | coffee |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | dancing | hiking  | woodworking | gardening | photography       |

