.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-5::.
There 6 different types of food: artichoke, lime, cucumber, cherry, pepper, potato
There are 6 different nationalities: german, spanish, turkish, canadian, malaysian, indonesian
1. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating pepper##2
2. the indonesian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
3. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
4. the indonesian is the person eating lime##1
5. the turkish is on the far right##1
6. the german is the person eating pepper##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
8. the malaysian is on the far left##1
9. the german is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
| Food          | potato | pepper | cucumber | artichoke | lime | cherry   |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | german   | spanish    | canadian | indonesian    | turkish |

