.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  paramedic, coach, manager, security-guard, fisherman, mechanic
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, basketball, baseball, ice-hockey, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 2. the paramedic is between the person who's sport is baseball and the mechanic##2
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the manager##1
 5. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
 7. the paramedic is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 9. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the coach is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | coach        | security-guard | mechanic | paramedic  | manager  | fisherman |
| Sport   | basketball | handball   | biathlon  | skiing | baseball | ice-hockey          |

