.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, cat, lizard, turtle, hamster, rabbit
The people use 6 different means of transport: roller, airplane, motorbike, bike, skateboard, helicopter
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the turtle##1
10. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the turtle and the person driving the airplane##2
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | rabbit | lizard      | turtle | hamster | cat | pony |
| Transport   | airplane  | roller | skateboard   | helicopter        | motorbike   | bike |

