 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |   3   |    4     |    5    |     6      |
