 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the owner of the fish is the malaysian##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the thai##3
 7. the french is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the french is on the right of the argentine##1
 9. the malaysian is between the argentine and the owner of the rat##2
10. the owner of the cat is the thai##1
11. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the egyptian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |    5     |     6     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | british | malaysian   | argentine | french |
| Pet           | dog    | cat    | rat   | fish | snake | ferret      |

