.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-10::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, coffee, tea, milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, water-polo, sailing, tennis, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
9. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4     |      5      |       6       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | milk | sprite     | tea    | fanta | coffee |
| Sport      | lacrosse | tennis   | sailing | water-polo | swimming    | skiing       |

