 4. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 6. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 8. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2   |   3    |   4    |      5      |     6     |
| Food   | apple | raspberry | lemon | cauliflower | cabbage | kiwi |
| Pet    | frog     | chinchilla | dog | lizard | pony         | rabbit       |

