3. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating kale##1
5. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
6. the person drinking cola is the person eating carrot##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |      3      |   4    |     5     |       6       |
