.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: house, r&b, soul, reggae, hip-hop, pop
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, german, chinese, pakistani, colombian, thai
 1. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 2. the fan of r&b is the thai##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the chinese##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the thai##3
 6. the fan of pop is on the left of the german##1
 7. the argentine is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 8. the german is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 9. the fan of soul is the chinese##1
10. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
11. the fan of reggae is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |     3      |    4    |    5     |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | soul   | hip-hop     | reggae    | pop     | house |
| Nationality   | thai  | chinese | argentine | colombian | pakistani | german   |

