 5. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person eating grapes is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
