.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-17::.
There 6 different types of food: papaya, broccoli, carrot, corn, tomato, apple
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, fantasy, superhero, family, musical, documentary
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 6. the person eating apple is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching family movies is the person eating apple##1
 8. the person eating carrot is between the person watching romance movies and the person eating corn##2
 9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |    5    |     6     |
| Food          | tomato     | carrot         | corn  | broccoli | papaya | apple |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | superhero | documentary | musical   | fantasy  | family    |

