.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, traveling, drawing, skydiving
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, climbing, weightlifting, lacrosse, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |    5    |      6      |
| Hobby   | camping | sudoku | traveling | drawing     | fishing | skydiving |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | weightlifting  | climbing   | skiing | lacrosse   | badminton    |

 